platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Double Fine’s riveting point-and-click adventure thrusts players into a timeless blend of whimsical sci-fi and dark fairy tale. Clever writing and stylish visuals keep its intersecting stories appealing—and at times, wickedly funny—with characters you’ll quickly become attached to (voiced by Elijah Wood, Jack Black, and other popular actors). Initially available with Act 1 only, Broken Age now includes the complete game—a one-of-a-kind odyssey that’s full of memorable moments.
